<br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d193c6324a9ba0aef223d7b99a8bbe77bf010aa5","tid":1544623,"uid":122723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"Steam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec1188a1ddea3b79830b7f0d5805278c0a6ca6a","tid":1544623,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:48:01.000Z","msg":"ps4lm"},{"pid":"1a689b526bda50aca6f88621ae81ef5b14de38c6","tid":1544623,"uid":134828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"點解仲未玩到嘅"},{"pid":"e3f655eb37ec06e53caf6f3117b22986d43a5b2b","tid":1544623,"uid":88231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"求各區報價"},{"pid":"60533caf34ea7171416c7201694401e8aa9127b1","tid":1544623,"uid":209883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"Download 唔到 有冇人都喺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"